name: Gold Sandstone sterling silver charm bracelet
description:
Various shapes of Gold Sandstone - unfaceted squares, faceted teardrops and faceted rondelles - are strung with sterling silver wire, like charms, on three sterling silver interlaced chains. Closed off with a beautiful sterling silver heart-shaped lobster claw clasp.
Approximate length is 7.25 inches.

name: Red Jasper square sterling silver bracelet
description:
Unfaceted Red Jasper squares and "Jet" Swarovski crystals are strung on stainless steel wire (for strength and flexibility). Sterling silver toggle closure.
Approximate length is 7.5 inches.

name: Green Jade sterling silver choker/necklace
description: Beautiful green Jade squares (dyed to enhance bright green color) along with Swarovski crystals and tiny sterling silver rondelles are strung together in a choker-style necklace on stainless steel wire (for strength and flexibility). Necklace is fully adjustable to be worn up to 16 inches long, while the Jade part extends about 9 inches around the neck. Sterling silver lobster clasp closure and three Swarovski crystals dangle from the back of the chain. All sterling silver.

name: Oval Carnelian sterling silver necklace
description:
Slightly faceted large Carnelian ovals are hand strung with sterling silver wire onto sterling silver square chain. Sterling silver toggle closure is attached to chain with two faceted Citrine rondelles.
Middle dangle length is approximately 2 inches.

name: Garnet & Iolite 14K yellow gold necklace
description:
Beautiful faceted Garnet and Iolite (dark blue stone) briolettes are handwrapped to a 14K gold diamond link chain. A larger faceted Iolite briolette and 14K yellow gold ball hang from a 2 inch dangle, adorned with more faceted Garnet briolettes and attached to the rest of the chain with a tiny faceted Iolite rondelle.
Tiny faceted Iolite rondelles connect the chain with the 14K yellow gold clasp in the back. All 14K yellow gold.
